DESCRIPTION: React component for visualizing stock price information with styling and dynamic icons.
SOURCE: https://github.com/assistant-ui/assistant-ui/blob/main/apps/docs/content/docs/runtimes/langgraph/tutorial/part-2.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_4

